All the section waitlists have some students on them and only one of the 5 section waitlists are full so it seems possible via telebears either by attempting to add the class (as it seems you have tried) or alternately selecting add to waitlist directly from your telebears homepage.

We are exploring whether or not we'll be able to expand 61C by another section in the summer. If that happens, we'll e-mail all waitlisted students to flag the new section's times and encourage folks to switch sections so that they can be enrolled.
